{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "biz-customer-service-conversation-office-af2z",
    "category": "pro/business/customer_service",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AF2z6gsN4G0",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh? Out of order.",
      "zh": "咦？故障了。",
      "ja": "え？故障してる。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm. Where is Stacy? I'll just use my favorite charging station.",
      "zh": "嗯，Stacy在哪裡？我就用我最喜歡的充電站吧。",
      "ja": "うーん。ステイシーはどこ？お気に入りの充電ステーションを使おう。",
      "time": "00:00:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh? Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh!",
      "zh": "咦？哦！哦！哦！哦！哦！哦！哦！",
      "ja": "え？ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh? What happened? Cleaning? What on earth is going on? Oh! Oh no!",
      "zh": "咦？發生什麼事了？清潔？到底發生什麼事？哦！糟了！",
      "ja": "え？何があったの？掃除？一体何が起こってるの？ああ！やばい！",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh! Oh!",
      "zh": "哦！哦！哦！哦！哦！哦！",
      "ja": "ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！ああ！",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kelly, find out where Kleenie is.",
      "zh": "Kelly，查查Kleenie在哪裡。",
      "ja": "ケリー、クリー二ーがどこにいるか調べて。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Roger!",
      "zh": "收到！",
      "ja": "了解！",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no, Kleenie!",
      "zh": "哦，不，Kleenie！",
      "ja": "ああ、クリー二ー！",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please stop!",
      "zh": "請停下！",
      "ja": "止まって！",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no!",
      "zh": "哦，不！",
      "ja": "やばい！",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no!",
      "zh": "哦，不！",
      "ja": "やばい！",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no!",
      "zh": "哦，不！",
      "ja": "やばい！",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no!",
      "zh": "哦，不！",
      "ja": "やばい！",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh-oh!",
      "zh": "喔喔！",
      "ja": "おっと！",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really strong!",
      "zh": "真的很強！",
      "ja": "本当に強い！",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "咦？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hm, Amber, you work with Heli to make sure that Queenie stays inside the square, and Roy and I will work on slowing him down.",
      "zh": "嗯，Amber，你和Heli一起確保Queenie待在方格內，Roy和我會努力減緩他的速度。",
      "ja": "うーん、アンバー、ヘリと協力してクイニーが四角の中にいるようにして、ロイと私は彼のスピードを落とすよ。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it!",
      "zh": "明白！",
      "ja": "了解！",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Roy, take him from the right side, and I'll get the left.",
      "zh": "Roy，你從右邊接他，我從左邊接。",
      "ja": "ロイ、右側から行って、私は左側を行く。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got him.",
      "zh": "抓到了。",
      "ja": "捕まえた。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got him.",
      "zh": "抓到了。",
      "ja": "捕まえた。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got him too!",
      "zh": "我也抓到了！",
      "ja": "私も捕まえた！",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think we can stop him by force.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們用武力無法阻止他。",
      "ja": "力ずくでは止められないと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's just too charged up.",
      "zh": "他太充滿能量了。",
      "ja": "彼はエネルギーが溢れすぎている。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In that case, we have to find a way for Queenie to use up his energy.",
      "zh": "那樣的話，我們得想辦法讓Queenie消耗他的能量。",
      "ja": "そういう場合は、クイニーにエネルギーを使わせる方法を見つけなければ。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A way for him to use up his energy?",
      "zh": "讓他消耗能量的方法？",
      "ja": "彼にエネルギーを使わせる方法？",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Huh!",
      "zh": "嗯！",
      "ja": "ええ！",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We should get him to the training track.",
      "zh": "我們應該帶他去訓練跑道。",
      "ja": "彼をトレーニングトラックに連れて行くべきだ。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He can burn all of this extra energy off safely there.",
      "zh": "他可以在那裡安全地消耗所有多餘的能量。",
      "ja": "そこで余分なエネルギーを安全に燃やせる。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's a good idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだ。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And how are we going to get Queenie over there?",
      "zh": "我們要怎麼帶Queenie過去？",
      "ja": "どうやってクイニーをそこに連れて行く？",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "zh": "別擔心。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just had another excellent idea.",
      "zh": "我剛想到另一個好主意。",
      "ja": "また素晴らしいアイデアが浮かんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everyone move out of the way!",
      "zh": "大家讓開！",
      "ja": "みんな、どいて！",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You need to speed up, Roy.",
      "zh": "你得加速，Roy。",
      "ja": "ロイ、スピードを上げて。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can't let Queenie catch up with you.",
      "zh": "你不能讓Queenie追上你。",
      "ja": "クイニーに追いつかれちゃだめだ。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey!",
      "zh": "哦，嘿！",
      "ja": "おっと、やあ！",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey!",
      "zh": "哦，嘿！",
      "ja": "おっと、やあ！",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey!",
      "zh": "哦，嘿！",
      "ja": "おっと、やあ！",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh!",
      "zh": "哦，哦，哦！",
      "ja": "おお、おお、おお！",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh!",
      "zh": "哦，哦，哦！",
      "ja": "おお、おお、おお！",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Queenie!",
      "zh": "Queenie！",
      "ja": "クイニー！",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh!",
      "zh": "哦，哦，哦，哦！",
      "ja": "おお、おお、おお、おお！",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who?",
      "zh": "誰？",
      "ja": "誰？",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I suppose I'm my number one.",
      "zh": "我想我是我的第一名。",
      "ja": "私は自分が一番だと思う。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, which way now?",
      "zh": "哦，現在往哪裡？",
      "ja": "ああ、今どっち？",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My number one favorite fruit.",
      "zh": "我最喜歡的水果第一名。",
      "ja": "私の一番好きな果物。",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不是。",
      "ja": "違う。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bananas are my number one favorite fruit.",
      "zh": "香蕉是我最喜歡的水果第一名。",
      "ja": "バナナが私の一番好きな果物。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The number one goes with bananas.",
      "zh": "第一名配香蕉。",
      "ja": "一番はバナナと一緒。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm off to Bananas Street.",
      "zh": "我要去香蕉街了。",
      "ja": "バナナ通りに行くよ。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nobody else is here yet.",
      "zh": "還沒有人來這裡。",
      "ja": "まだ誰もいない。",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey!",
      "zh": "哦，嘿！",
      "ja": "おっと、やあ！",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're almost done.",
      "zh": "我們快完成了。",
      "ja": "もうすぐ終わる。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And Max never showed up.",
      "zh": "Max從未出現。",
      "ja": "マックスは来なかった。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why didn't he make it here?",
      "zh": "他為什麼沒來？",
      "ja": "なぜここに来なかったの？",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sure he completely forgot again.",
      "zh": "我確定他又完全忘了。",
      "ja": "きっとまた完全に忘れたんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh!",
      "zh": "哦，哦，哦！",
      "ja": "ああ、ああ、ああ！",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I must have fallen asleep.",
      "zh": "我一定睡著了。",
      "ja": "寝ちゃったに違いない。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where's everybody else?",
      "zh": "其他人在哪裡？",
      "ja": "みんなはどこ？",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "あれは何？",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a fire!",
      "zh": "著火了！",
      "ja": "火事だ！",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fire!",
      "zh": "火災！",
      "ja": "火事！",
      "time": "00:06:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The entire forest is going to burn down.",
      "zh": "整個森林都要燒毀了。",
      "ja": "森全体が燃えちゃう。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do I do?",
      "zh": "我該怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "どうしよう？",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Think, Max, think.",
      "zh": "想想，Max，想想。",
      "ja": "考えろ、マックス、考えろ。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have to alert the rescue team.",
      "zh": "我得通知救援隊。",
      "ja": "救助隊に知らせなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, come on.",
      "zh": "唉，拜託。",
      "ja": "ああ、頼むよ。",
      "time": "00:06:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where did I put the key to the garage?",
      "zh": "我把車庫鑰匙放哪了？",
      "ja": "ガレージの鍵どこに置いた？",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Kelly, I think it's time you talk about Kelly's way.",
      "zh": "Kelly，我想是時候談談Kelly的方法了。",
      "ja": "ケリー、ケリーの方法について話す時だと思う。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Go ask Max.",
      "zh": "去問Max。",
      "ja": "マックスに聞いてきて。",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You told me it's silly.",
      "zh": "你說那很傻。",
      "ja": "バカみたいだって言ったよね。",
      "time": "00:06:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Go ask Max?",
      "zh": "去問Max？",
      "ja": "マックスに聞いてきて？",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He told me he was having trouble remembering things.",
      "zh": "他告訴我他記憶有困難。",
      "ja": "彼は物覚えが悪いって言ってた。",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So I told him about Heli's way.",
      "zh": "所以我告訴他Heli的方法。",
      "ja": "だからヘリの方法を教えたんだ。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "咦？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fine.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I guess I'll just have to go ask Max.",
      "zh": "我想我只能去問Max了。",
      "ja": "マックスに聞きに行くしかないね。",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "咦？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "咦？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You've reached the rescue team.",
      "zh": "你已聯絡到救援隊。",
      "ja": "救助隊に繋がりました。",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can go quick.",
      "zh": "可以快點來嗎？",
      "ja": "早く来てください。",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The forest is on fire.",
      "zh": "森林著火了。",
      "ja": "森が火事です。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Give me your exact location so we can get you some help.",
      "zh": "告訴我你確切的位置，好讓我們派人救援。",
      "ja": "正確な場所を教えてください、助けに行きます。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, they don't know exactly where I am.",
      "zh": "哦，他們不知道我確切在哪。",
      "ja": "ああ、私の正確な場所がわからない。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't know how time to search every forest in Bruce Town.",
      "zh": "我不知道他們有多少時間去找布魯斯鎮的每個森林。",
      "ja": "ブルースタウンの森を全部探す時間があるかわからない。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Think carefully.",
      "zh": "仔細想想。",
      "ja": "よく考えて。",
      "time": "00:07:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I care.",
      "zh": "我在意。",
      "ja": "気にしてる。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I care remember.",
      "zh": "我記得我在意。",
      "ja": "気にしてたのを覚えてる。",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, Max, do you remember seeing anything along your way?",
      "zh": "嘿，Max，你記得路上有看到什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "ねえ、マックス、道中で何か見なかった？",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me think.",
      "zh": "讓我想想。",
      "ja": "考えさせて。",
      "time": "00:07:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah, I saw any eating of banana in her front yard.",
      "zh": "哦，是的，我看到有人在她家前院吃香蕉。",
      "ja": "ああ、彼女の前庭でバナナを食べているのを見たよ。",
